105
00:08:48,442 --> 00:08:49,443
Rosetta?

106
00:08:50,361 --> 00:08:51,653
Aion!

107
00:08:58,410 --> 00:08:59,244
Chrno.

108
00:09:02,748 --> 00:09:03,582
Chrno!

109
00:09:05,918 --> 00:09:06,835
