118
00:09:45,332 --> 00:09:50,670
Postarám sa o sestru.
Keď získaš Joshuu,choď po Rosettu.

119
00:09:53,423 --> 00:09:54,174
Nabiť!

120
00:09:56,218 --> 00:09:57,177
