121
00:09:58,011 --> 00:10:00,347
ako vínná réva pred zberom.

122
00:10:02,349 --> 00:10:04,059
Úrodný október!

123
00:10:06,853 --> 00:10:08,939
Plodná libra!

124
00:10:22,827 --> 00:10:26,623
