133
00:11:08,915 --> 00:11:09,874
Nabiť.

134
00:11:23,888 --> 00:11:25,223
Sestra!

135
00:11:26,766 --> 00:11:29,352
Sestra!Sestra!

136
00:11:29,978 --> 00:11:31,187
Neboj sa.

137
00:11:32,355 --> 00:11:36,150
Ochránim ťa.

138
00:11:36,609 --> 00:11:40,697
Sestra!Sestra!

139
00:11:43,616 --> 00:11:48,037
Určite...celkom určite ťa ochránim.

140
00:11:48,913 --> 00:11:52,750
