165
00:13:55,622 --> 00:13:56,665
Aion...

166
00:13:58,417 --> 00:14:00,002
Poďme už.

167
00:14:00,419 --> 00:14:01,461
Ako si praješ.

168
00:14:19,396 --> 00:14:20,397
Chrno!

169
00:14:27,446 --> 00:14:29,531
Čo je on?On nie je normálny!

170
00:14:30,532 --> 00:14:32,409
