179
00:14:55,599 --> 00:14:57,183
Zabite ho!

180
00:14:57,183 --> 00:14:59,853
Čo?!Má na sebe znak Magdaléniek!

181
00:15:00,186 --> 00:15:01,021
Tadiaľto.

182
00:15:01,146 --> 00:15:02,105
Uteká!

183
00:15:02,188 --> 00:15:03,148
Za ním!

184
00:15:24,294 --> 00:15:27,005
Sestra,prosím prestaň!

185
00:15:27,672 --> 00:15:31,843
Tvoja sestra Floretta zomrela pred 10timi rokmi.

186
00:15:33,678 --> 00:15:37,849
Som lovec ktorý sa zrodil z Floretty.

187
00:15:38,975 --> 00:15:43,605
